I was under mentorship of Chartered Accountant Kushal
Raj during this internship.My interest in fintech got me
this internship.The main part of this summer internship is
exploring and finding tech solutions for work efficiency.It
also enhanced my knowledge in finance and accounting.
My Contributions:
● Automated creation of audit appointment and
engagement letter(Python)
● Created whatsapp automation excel template to
intimate all clients in one click(VBA)
● After thorough observations and brainstorming, I
suggested the idea of using RPA(Robotic Process
Automation) for monotonous tasks at the office.
